Distribution:

 This game is public domain software. This means, you may copy
 and spread it for any non-commercial purposes.

 I have to make one single exception for Germany:
 Mr. Stefan Ossowski is not allowed to copy, offer or sell this
 game.


Vertrieb:

 Dieses Spiel ist Public Domain Software. Das bedeutet, daß Sie
 es für nicht gewerbliche Zwecke sooft kopieren und weitergeben
 dürfen, wie Sie wollen.

 Für Deutschland mache ich allerdings folgende Einschränkung:
 Der PD-Versand Stefan Ossowski darf dieses Spiel weder kopieren,
 anbieten, noch verkaufen.


Version:

 This is the English version of EMPOROS - THE TRADE. There is
 also existing a German one. You can find it on the following
 disks:

           1) DACG-PDS-3
           2) FRANZ-PD-29

 You can get the first one at:

                         DACG-Computerclub eV
                         Postfach 30
                         D-2811 Martfeld

 Achtung! Es existiert noch eine deutsche Version von
 EMPOROS - THE TRADE. Sie können diese auf den oben angegebenen
 Disks beim DACG-Computerclub eV bekommen.


The Story:

 You are living on the island Emporos, where several countries do
 exist. Your job is to make one of these countries your own. There
 is only one way to do this - and you have to find it out.


Translations:

 I'd like to do translations of Amiga-programs from English to German.
 This would support the popularity of English & American software
 in Germany.
 I will do this job for commercial and non-commercial purposes. Maybe
 my English is not the best, but my German surely is. Contact me.

                                                Roland

